<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #F0EDE5; /* Nude color for the background */
        }

        nav {
            background-color: #f2e9d0; /* Nude color for the background */
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        li {
            display: inline;
            margin-right: 20px;
        }

        a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #7E7A73; /* Nude color for the text */
            padding: 10px 20px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        a:hover {
            color: #3D3B35; /* Darker color on hover */
        }

        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            color: #3D3B35;
            font-size: 40px; /* Adjust the font size as needed */
        }

        h4 {
            text-align: center;
            color: #3D3B35;
            font-size: 20px; /* Adjust the font size as needed */
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 50px 20px;
            align-items: center; /* Align items vertically */
        }

        .left-side {
            text-align: left;
            padding-right: 20px; /* Add some space between the text and image */
        }

        .right-side {
            text-align: right;
            padding-left: 20px; /* Add some space between the text and image */
        }

        .container img {
            width: 250px; /* Adjust the width of the image */
            height: auto; /* Maintain aspect ratio */
            border-radius: 50%; /* Make the image round */
            vertical-align: middle; /* Align the image vertically */
        }

        .lorem-info {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .moving-image {
            position: fixed;
            width: 150px;
            height: auto;
            bottom: 0; /* Position at the bottom of the screen */
            right: 0; /* Start position at the left edge */
            animation: moveImage 5s linear infinite; /* Animation properties */
        }

        @keyframes moveImage {
            0% {
                right: 0; /* Starting position */
            }
            100% {
                right: calc(100% - 50px); /* Ending position */
            }
        }

        nav ul li:nth-child(2) a {
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #F0EDE5;
            padding: 50px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="./home">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="./about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="./portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
            <li><a href="./game">Game</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="left-side">
            <h1> <%= name %> </h1>
            <h4> <%= school  %> </h4>
            <h4> <%= email  %> </h4>
        </div>
        <div class="right-side">
            <img src="https://scontent.fmnl17-5.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-9/48386779_2154308901458373_5698394108175843328_n.jpg?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=7a1959&_nc_eui2=AeHXmyugzPqRbQhgtaPCkX_52OVcxN3PsyTY5VzE3c-zJEH41TBXjSbbLfUXPAqmXvH6egxXus81j1WjWWKfFm17&_nc_ohc=GPQj_F4y63UAX-6Uim8&_nc_ht=scontent.fmnl17-5.fna&oh=00_AfDJpiYhpACE2NC-aPdzxVe7mdGoLSkuvy03_9se2zpfAQ&oe=65FD304A" alt="PROFILE PICTURE" class="profile-picture">
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="lorem-info">
        <p>I am Kristine Angela A. Gallawan,</p>
        <p>A 3rd Year Student at Ateneo de Davao University</p>
        <p>At hindi nila alam na isa pala akong anak ng Mafia Boss</p>
        <p>And I believe in the saying that the children are our future</p>
        <p>Teach them well and let them lead the way</p>
        <p>Show them all the beauty they possess inside</p>
        <p>Give them a sense of pride to make it easier</p>
        <p>Let the children's laughter remind us how we used to be</p>
        <p>And I, Thank you!</p>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <img src="https://media.tenor.com/TT1hCsF1vUwAAAAi/banana-cat-running.gif" alt="Moving Image" class="moving-image">
    </footer>
    
</body>

</html>
